snippet.title: Resident Evil Village - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Fear surrounds you in Resident Evil Village, unleashing a new chapter of survival horror on PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X, and PC in 2021!


For more official news and updates, follow us on:
Twitter - https://twitter.com/RE_Games
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/residentevil/
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/re_games/
